  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Cut the phyllo dough into 4 equal pieces. Roll each piece into a ball and then flatten into a disk.",
    "In a pan over medium heat, sauté the onion, cilantro, ginger, garlic, cumin, coriander, turmeric, and salt until the onion is translucent.",
    "Stir in the Venezuelan cheese until it's well combined with the spice mixture.",
    "Place a tablespoon of the filling in the center of each phyllo disk.",
    "Fold the dough into a triangle, pressing the edges to seal.",
